    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This specification defines the WebFinger protocol, which can be used to discover information about people or other entities on the Internet using standard HTTP methods.  WebFinger discovers information for a URI that might not be usable as a locator otherwise, such as account or email URIs.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
